<view style="padding: 32px">
  <van-image
    width="100%"
    height="700rpx"
    fit="contain"
    src="/static/qr.jpg"
    show-menu-by-longpress
  />
  <view style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 20rpx">
    <view>1. 长按图片关注公众号</view>
    <view>2. 点击刷新按钮</view>
    <view style="color: #999; font-size: 12px">
      如果已关注公众号、刷新后仍停留在该页面，请先取消关注公众号，再重复步骤1、步骤2
    </view>

    <van-button type="primary" block bind:click="refresh"> 刷新 </van-button>
  </view>
</view>
